description:
This award-winning turkey breast that has been roasted to perfection, serve this with a homemade cranberry sauce and use leftovers in a wrap or salad. 

Average weight of this product varies between 2.2KG - 3.2KG.Please note the price shown is calculated based on the maximum weight. 
This is a variable weight product and is priced by $/kg. Once we?ve picked your item in store, we?ll refund you for the difference between the weight paid and the weight received. 
Make sure you utilise our pickers notes in the check out to add weight recommendations for our store pickers. We will try our best to provide you with the requested weight. 

Oven Heating Instructions: 
Heating times are a guide and may vary depending on your appliance. 

1. Preheat oven to 180°C (Fan Forced 160°C). 
2. Remove product from packaging before heating. 
3. Place in a pan with a little water. Cover with foil. 
4. Heat for approximately 30 minutes per kg. 
Storeage instructions:
Keep refrigereated at 1 - 5 C. Once opened, use within 3 days.
